abstract: The auxiliary of the New York Infirmary will benefit from the Champagne Ball at the St. Regis-Sheraton Roof on Friday. Mrs. Robert F. Wagner and Mrs. Eric B. Outwater are honorary chairmen for the event. Proceeds will be used for the hospital's nursery.
